    "en": "Three are the closest of creation to Allah, Mighty and Majestic, on the Day of Resurrection until He completes the Reckoning: a man whose power in the state of his anger does not lead him to oppress those under his authority; a man who walks between two and does not lean toward one of them over the other by even a barleycorn; and a man who speaks the truth whether it is against him or in his favor.",
